":class:`~scrapy.downloadermiddlewares.offsite.OffsiteMiddleware` uses it to "
"allow requests to domains not in :attr:`~scrapy.Spider.allowed_domains`. To "
"skip only the offsite filter without affecting other components, consider "
"using the :reqmeta:`allow_offsite` request meta key instead."
